data.text:
Two Of The Hottest Headliners In Country

After wowing fans in 2016, Lee Brice and Justin Moore are continue their mammoth co-headline American Made Tour into 2017! These stetson-toting gentlemen make for perfect touring partners with their heady mix of upbeat country rock and pop, so don't miss them when they hit in , ,

Touted as the small town dreamer with a heart of gold, Justin Moore wowed the critics with his self-titled debut in 2009. Mixing a traditional country aesthetic with a contemporary sound, Moore's expressive vocals and Arkansas twang seal the deal! Fellow country crooner Lee Brice similarly stormed the Nashville scene with four number one singles on the Billboard charts to date. The South Carolina born heartthrob combines old school honky tonk with a rugged rock 'n roll style.
